-0->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice-1->cartservice-0\",\n    \"frontend-0->cartservice-2\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HMSET, HGET 请求延迟增加\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmptyCart, GetCart 请求延迟增加\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上结果是基于调用链拓扑和统计数据得出的，请确认相关服务组件的性能监控以进一步分析可能的根因。"}
